CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, page 21, reads: "The Frankfort Distillers booth displayer Four Roses and passed out souvenirs. The company was represented by Phil Thomas, Bud Bell, and Bob Ewing."
TitMainTitle: Two men standing, possibly including Phil Thomas, Bud Bell, or Bob Ewing, in Frankfort Distillers Corporation booth featuring Four Roses whiskey in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
